title: GO SMS PRO Spring Super Theme
creator: GO Launcher EX

extendedInfo.description: Here comes our Hello Spring Super Theme for GO SMS Pro with amazing effects when touching, sliding, pressing and shaking.The winter of 2012 is going, and the we are to meet the 2013 spring, can you feel the breath of the nature?â¤ Main effectsBackground will switch on sunny day and rainy day every 17 seconds.> Sunny scene: Click or slide the screen will appear petals             Butterfly flies in the grass             Shake the phone, the flowers and grass at the bottom will sway and some petals will fly up> Rainy scene: Click or slide the screen, then the screen will appear some raindrops;            Clouds rolling, thunder lightning            Shake the phone, the flowers and grass at the bottom will sway, and the raindrops will fall from skyPlease read below notice carefully, thanks!â¤ Notice1. Please make sure your GO SMS Pro is v4.73 or above. (You can download from Google Play market)2.
